reviews.text:
This was a surprisingly cozy cafe with a very extensive menu.
The local is very clean and the.service was quite good.
The food was quite tasty and priced ok. It was also much more quiet than I would have expected.
Only caveat, the salad was served in a weird fancy plate that cause the food to slide off to one side onto the table. Terrible choice of plate!

Western food is always my first pick when I have to decide on a place for dinner, today...we came over to this restaurant as we have heard a lot of good things about it. 

The environment itself is very spacious yet mordern, there are lights projecting on the wall, which makes it funky and the bar was an open bar which serves drinks. 

We ordered a snack platter and a dinner set to share. The snack platter consists of fried oyster, honey chicken wings, salad and onion rings. A good start for the meal. The dinner set consist of a soup, main and dessert. We added extra for their famous popcorn coffee, it was on the sweeter side. The soup was mushroom cream soup which tasted quite filling and smooth. We ordered the pork with apple sauce as our main course. It was well cooked and the apple sauce added a special taste to the dish; giving it a nice touch. 

Last but not least, the dessert was orange flavor cheese cake with orange bits! It’s actually my first try, it was a good ending to the meal.
Very limited selection, taste standard n very local
Food is good. Service OK. You need a mobile phone with QR Code app to read the menu.
Staff were not attentive..food was just ok

Only caveat, the salad was served in a weird fancy plate that cause the food to slide off to one side onto the table. Terrible choice of plate!

店舖內外100分，美食服務拿滿分

長沙灣食過的茶餐廳多，酒樓拉麵也多，早前看過雜誌介紹一間名字特別的西餐廳，兩口子今晚終於能在晚上訂位一試😙

餐廳名字叫Fifty Fifty，唔深究真的不知道原來老闆想廚房做到50分樓面做到50分，內外加埋就是滿分100分👍 落單前先擦擦檯面上的QR Code, 看看細心的環保Menu這個時段有咩選擇先，既衛生又清晰👏

首先推介，亦都係專為高CP的它而來的黑松露醬大啡菇😍，如圖所見絕對足料的大啡菇賣相已經引死人👍，所以專誠切埋比你睇睇佢個菇內外都係50+50真材實料! juicy得誇張🤣

第二個頭盤選了香煎法國鵝肝配焦糖蘋果，鵝肝一大塊外脆內軟，可能係我倆太喜愛鵝肝關係，兩個人食這個鵝肝有點未夠喉(太好食了吧)🤣👍 所以如果兩人叫兩個豪食也算值得的😝

第三個頭盤是炸小食併盤有炸蠔(juicy)、炸魷魚圈、炸蝦及單骨雞翼，食哂呢三個頭盤已經差唔多比滿分👏

終於到Main Course! 鮮馬拉蜆香蒜白酒墨魚汁意粉😮，蜆是意外地大隻鮮甜，墨魚汁味道足料九少許胡椒味，值得一試。

來多一個必會飽肚的日本帶子海膽意大利飯，暖暖意大利飯濃味不膩，海膽與飯二合為一讓整個味道提升，貪心的我覺得如果再多一粒帶子的話那就是完美😂

茉莉花水果茶，香口濃茶有花香水果微酸，入口舒服解渴👍
每款菜式均可以追加$20轉為套餐，有餐湯餐飲甜品，可以說是非常超值👏

👅美味: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️/5

💡性價: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️/5
💆‍♂️服務: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️/5
撇除老人家幫襯，需二維碼睇餐單，地方吾錯，食物出品吾自太差

路經這裡見到這間西餐廳，想不到深水埗有這般優雅的西餐廳，睇過餐牌價錢不貴，入去試試

好特別，無餐牌給我們，枱上有張紙有個QR code（二圍碼），用電話掃一下就可以看到餐牌，好高科技

是日餐湯-雜菜海鮮湯，頗特別，忌廉湯加入海鮮同雜菜，有少少番茄的酸味，但又很creamy

燒牛肉意大利麵包-意大利麵包烘過再加入燒到半熟的燒牛肉，沙律醬同生菜，簡單的食材，但組合起來就成為頂級美食

炸鱈魚全日早餐-炸鱈魚柳，炒蛋，番茄，煙三文魚，大啡菇，意大利麵包，沙律菜，好豐富，好大份！炸鱈魚柳，外脆，內嫩滑，超好味

炭燒豬鞍全日早餐-除左由鱈魚柳換成炭燒豬鞍，其他東西是一樣的，豬鞍唔韌又多汁

芒果梳打- 有原粒芒果
檸檬荔枝梳打- 同樣有原粒茘枝，而且個荔枝糖漿超好味

是日蛋糕：士多啤梨芝士蛋糕- 質感有點像紐約芝士蛋糕，硬身而芝士味濃，當中夾了少許士多啤梨果肉，同餅面加了焦糖醬，令味道很豐富

Western food is always my first pick when I have to decide on a place for dinner, today...we came over to this restaurant as we have heard a lot of good things about it. 

The environment itself is very spacious yet mordern, there are lights projecting on the wall, which makes it funky and the bar was an open bar which serves drinks. 

We ordered a snack platter and a dinner set to share. The snack platter consists of fried oyster, honey chicken wings, salad and onion rings. A good start for the meal. The dinner set consist of a soup, main and dessert. We added extra for their famous popcorn coffee, it was on the sweeter side. The soup was mushroom cream soup which tasted quite filling and smooth. We ordered the pork with apple sauce as our main course. It was well cooked and the apple sauce added a special taste to the dish; giving it a nice touch. 

Last but not least, the dessert was orange flavor cheese cake with orange bits! It’s actually my first try, it was a good ending to the meal.
